
### show available models (ollama list)
GET http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/tags

### Muestra los modelos de Ubuntu (Remotos)
GET http://192.168.100.33:11434/api/tags

### Remote models (ngrok)
GET https://2419-2806-2f0-a6a0-dae4-c0b6-6674-d14-ebdd.ngrok-free.app/api/tags

### Show running models
GET http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/ps

### Show model information 
POST http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/show
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "llama3.2",
  "details": true
}


### Delete a model
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:11434/api/delete
Content-Type: application/json

{ 
  "model": "llama3.2"
}